scene.message:
Ayase: Whaaat?!{nl}
Did Ayase just beat those{nl}
guys up?!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You too, Ayase...{wait_fr:21}{nl}
What's going on{nl}
here?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What?{nl}
Ayase doesn't understand{nl}
any of this!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Allow me to explain.{nl}
Though, what we know{nl}
is fairly limited.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: So...{wait_fr:16}{nl}
what am I supposed to{nl}
do with this power?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Sitting here won't{nl}
solve anything,{wait_fr:16}{nl}
let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: So you're the same{nl}
as Yuka — feels like{nl}
fate!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: This is incredible...{nl}
Like something out{nl}
of sci-fi...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
beyond here — if you{nl}
see anything suspicious,{nl}
think first!{waitkey}{clearbox}...Honestly,{nl}
just thinking about{nl}
Inaba still{nl}
makes me furious!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: It feels like{nl}
someone's pulling our{nl}
strings — awful feeling!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: This is amazing...{nl}
To build something like this —{nl}
they mean business.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase doesn't{nl}
really get any of this...{nl}
So much happening at once.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ugh...{nl}
Ayase feels sick...{wait_fr:21}{nl}
One of those is{nl}
inside me?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Oh yeah! This tension!{nl}
This is what I live for —{nl}
watch me shine!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: There must be lots{nl}
of Demons deeper in...{nl}
How wonderful.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: We need to catch{nl}
Mr. Kandori before{nl}
it's too late!{waitkey}{ret}
